                    "line_text": "Comme une toile d'araignée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Où vont se prendre les soleils.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Oui, sois de plus en plus géante,\nEt devant la foule béante\nQue charmeront tes fils vermeils,\nApparais, de clarté baignée,\nComme une toile d'araignée\nOù vont se prendre les soleils."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Pendant les prochaines semailles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Luis, resplendis avec tes mailles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Brille, joyau prestigieux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Et séduis l'œil par ta caresse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Filigrane ajouré, que tresse",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Un orfèvre prodigieux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pendant les prochaines semailles,\nLuis, resplendis avec tes mailles,\nBrille, joyau prestigieux\nEt séduis l'œil par ta caresse,\nFiligrane ajouré, que tresse\nUn orfèvre prodigieux."
        },
        {
