                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Le hardi faucon, le gerfaut,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Les vautours, les aigles voraces ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Mais en contemplant ces terrasses,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Ils trouveront que c'est trop haut.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "On verra, dans leurs vols énormes,\nAccourir vers tes plates-formes\nLe hardi faucon, le gerfaut,\nLes vautours, les aigles voraces ;\nMais en contemplant ces terrasses,\nIls trouveront que c'est trop haut."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Monte encor, Tour démesurée !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Le dieu de la mer azurée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Et de l'ouragan libyen,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Dit à l'équipe ralliée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "De Babel réconciliée :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Venez, à présent. Je veux bien.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Monte encor, Tour démesurée !\nLe dieu de la mer azurée\nEt de l'ouragan libyen,\nDit à l'équipe ralliée\nDe Babel réconciliée :\nVenez, à présent. Je veux bien."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "La Tour grandit et, sur son faîte,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Invincible, dressant la tête,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "L'Homme ouvrant tout grands ses yeux clairs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Pourra, dans ses jeux ordinaires,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Prendre dans ses mains les tonnerres",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Et jouer avec les éclairs.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La Tour grandit et, sur son faîte,\nInvincible, dressant la tête,\nL'Homme ouvrant tout grands ses yeux clairs,\nPourra, dans ses jeux ordinaires,\nPrendre dans ses mains les tonnerres\nEt jouer avec les éclairs."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Car, autrefois chaste et jalouse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Maintenant, la Science épouse",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "L'Homme et, regardant l'Orient,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Pour lui déchire tous les voiles",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Qui lui dérobaient les étoiles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Et baise sa bouche, en riant.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Car, autrefois chaste et jalouse,\nMaintenant, la Science épouse\nL'Homme et, regardant l'Orient,\nPour lui déchire tous les voiles\nQui lui dérobaient les étoiles,\nEt baise sa bouche, en riant."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Sans craindre que rien la meurtrisse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "La Science libératrice,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Dans sa main tenant une faux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Que l'on ne voyait pas naguère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Moissonnera les deuils, la guerre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Les canons et les échafauds.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sans craindre que rien la meurtrisse,\nLa Science libératrice,\nDans sa main tenant une faux\nQue l'on ne voyait pas naguère,\nMoissonnera les deuils, la guerre,\nLes canons et les échafauds."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Tour, grand lys fleuri dans l'espace,",
