                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Épouvantant le doute amer,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Les certitudes et l'extase",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Reviendront caresser ta base,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Comme les vagues d'une mer.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tour, grand lys fleuri dans l'espace,\nColosse de force et de grâce !\nÉpouvantant le doute amer,\nLes certitudes et l'extase\nReviendront caresser ta base,\nComme les vagues d'une mer."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Et, malgré le vent, qui s'effare,",
